rmal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925ad32d32b2e8115a139063da15e5cdab4e1dc8","tid":437892,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食紅衫果食斑咪冇乜骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但老一輩成日講多骨先甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw我覺得豬羊雞都係近骨位先好食</blockquote><br />\n但係你食豬羊雞起碼有得避開啲骨位然後一啖肉其啖飯咁食吖，比著你夜晚食鯇魚，lur完骨人哋都食完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n況且又冇得送飯，有時個口仲有啲飯然之後食魚有骨真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9025de7e737a865fba02f7afeeac35960555400","tid":437892,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"同埋唔食魚除咗會有大頸泡之外仲有冇其他問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe9665fde16e5b4c537b6eb359fad0b04c936e7","tid":437892,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"really?"},{"pid":"67ade08453ec1190638968a7b76aa04f6284661f","tid":437892,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"大家不妨講吓點解唔鍾意食"},{"pid":"4d0620c373559d9c8c3bbf1173f8c2175481d8bd","tid":437892,"uid":89608,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"靚魚, 又鮮又嫩, 不知幾正, <br />\n<br />\n唔食魚人生少一大享受"},{"pid":"b3cc37c042618dea512ec148c16e7090ad70e2c6","tid":437892,"uid":102456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"睇得出樓主中意腐皮多過魚好很多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dc8567751d24fed442e53b7c64974ff9e792f3","tid":437892,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T23:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚魚, 又鮮又嫩, 不知幾正, <br />\n<br />\n唔食魚人生少一大享受</blockquote><br />\n鮮嫩但係多骨<br />\n只可以細細啖咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/n